{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782260845678,"sessionID":"ses_108fa29f5ffefS4AJ2RxMtfdwn","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"427456859","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Cache API\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance with a Map-based storage structure.\n\n```javascript\nimport { createCache } from './cache.mjs'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\nReturns an object containing the following methods:\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by key.\n\n- **Parameter:**\n  - `key` - The cache key to look up\n  \n- **Returns:** The cached value if found, otherwise `undefined`\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nSets the given value in the cache.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The cache key\n  - `value` - The value to cache\n  \n- **Returns:** The value that was set\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a value from the cache.\n\n- **Parameter:**\n  - `key` - The cache key to remove\n  \n- **Returns:** `true` if the key existed and was removed, `false` otherwise\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n- **Returns:** `undefined`\n","filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-23T16-47-14-546Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-23T16-47-14-546Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","exists":false,"truncated":false,"tokenwarden":{"wouldHaveUsedTokens":6,"usedTokens":6,"savedTokens":0,"percentSaved":0,"rawPath":"/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-23T16-47-14-546Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-3/tokenwarden/encrypted/raw-tool-output/ses_108fa29f5ffefS4AJ2RxMtfdwn/427456859.txt.enc","event":{"timestamp":"2026-06-24T00:27:25.653Z","sessionID":"ses_108fa29f5ffefS4AJ2RxMtfdwn","source":"tool-output","label":"write","wouldHaveUsedTokens":6,"usedTokens":6,"savedTokens":0,"percentSaved":0,"metadata":{"callID":"427456859","rawPath":"/tmp/tokenw